{"tid":874233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳君如經典爆seed串爆劉華大快人心！！！","createTime":"2018-10-24T05:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T16:03:11.000Z","uid":82917,"like":356,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9164326a43b66f418151e5babe49954baa4019","tid":874233,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BX1U2-LnL50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBX1U2-LnL50&d=PLqY17On9GjrtTpqPr5A8QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b77dc1b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BX1U2-LnL50</a><br />\n「劉德華好勁架！咁大年紀都可以搞大人地個肚，我真係好。。。好crazy呀！！！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/125929_a18f6749437a252c0519147eede9779b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F125929_a18f6749437a252c0519147eede9779b.png&h=f7c4c404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗係得吳君如咁有吉士敢係頒獎禮上公然串到佢一棟都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劉華心諗：你個八婆好嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/125942_d350a939cc62c3faa0670b87d6b02561.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F125942_d350a939cc62c3faa0670b87d6b02561.png&h=5799015c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而劉嘉玲係隔離只能尷尬一笑，完全禁佢唔住<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/130001_0edd044a530dbf1ac20a653146e06ee3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F130001_0edd044a530dbf1ac20a653146e06ee3.png&h=ae01f121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉青雲同郭藹明個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/130004_17042e4110545053bd56ad59211f0ebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F130004_17042e4110545053bd56ad59211f0ebc.png&h=d3923cd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbc44704de5ec624ab1cbfabe220682c4d044d6d","tid":874233,"uid":82917,"like":323,"dislike":1,"score":322,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"紅都耳哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/130236_d132acd163ec4e1a8786751ccf0598dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F130236_d132acd163ec4e1a8786751ccf0598dd.png&h=de72687d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9759d19ad1f9786813c263dfb9306e7da50e3c8d","tid":874233,"uid":58140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快人快語"},{"pid":"50a56d922117543345570b3ef90126523dedfcb0","tid":874233,"uid":82917,"like":338,"dislike":1,"score":337,"quote":{"pid":"9759d19ad1f9786813c263dfb9306e7da50e3c8d","tid":874233,"uid":58140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快人快語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"劉華一開始仲笑笑口以為吳君如又交行貨讚佢靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184ee9a3214e3bc1caf732cf66a93a5d0eb6a4b2","tid":874233,"uid":78971,"like":175,"dislike":1,"score":174,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"劉青雲好似講緊：嘩精彩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" 